definitions.definition: A market town and civil parish with a town council in the Metropolitan Borough of Leeds , West Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE2045 ) .
A village and civil parish in East Suffolk district, Suffolk , England ( OS grid ref TM2055 ) .
An unincorporated community in Marion County , Iowa , United States .
A habitational surname from Old English .
